svg.text: People living with disabilities face discrimination when trying to access work and also in-work bias.The main problem they encounter at work is stereotypes and labelling:

text.tspan: Filaments Bamboo Weaving is the first batch of China's National Intangible Cultural Heritage.

svg.text: Bamboo weaving is rustic and unfashionable.
Few people understand or enjoy bamboo weaving works.
The craftsmanship of bamboo weaving is highly demanding yet with low return.
Few people are willing to dedicate themselves to learning and preserving the Intangible Cultural Heritage of Filaments Bamboo Weaving.
They are not as productive as non-disabled people
They are waiting for help from others
